

webapp
  - lapis creating pages
  - api with lru cache, shdict cache

imghost
  nginx running on server with gluster fs providing redundancy
  servers images
  accepts new uploads from imgprocess
  eventually accepts user uploaded imageLinks

imgprocess
 - checks for new links
 - scrapes the page for images
 special pages:
  imgur
   - use api to get album/image icon
  youtube
   - use youtube icon link


